{
  "text": "The patients with diabetes were identified by the following inclusion criteria of which at least one criteria had to be met: A) At least one glycated hemoglobin (HbA1c) value \u22656.6% (\u226548.6 mmol/mol) registered in the Clinical Laboratory Information System (LABKA), [CITATION_1] Based on the above-mentioned four criteria, the eligible study participants for the diabetes sample comprised of 14,831 patients who potentially might suffer from diabetes, of whom 3,345 were excluded due to age under 25 or age above 75 years.",
